        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks WBC for his account of glacial action in Australia. A mundane cooler period would throw a flood of light on geographical distribution. Has sketched a large MS on subject but does not know whether he will live to publish it.</p>
            <p>Questions WBC on striated granite boulders.</p>
            <p>Asks him to make a botanical experiment on insect fertilisation.</p>
        </abstract>
